'''Mask''' (IPAc-en mɒsk; frah المسجد ''Al-masjid'') a plies a woship fi falara a [[Izlam|Izlam]].

A schrik ah ditiel rikuayament ina [[Suni Izlam|Suni]] ''fiqh'' fi a plies a woship fi bi kansida mask, wid plies we no miit demya rikuayament rigyaad az ''musalla''.<ref name="qaSunniPathFiqhMasjid">[http://qa.sunnipath.com/issue_view.asp?HD=1&ID=4347&CATE=4/ Fiqh of Masjid & Musalla] Qa.sunnipath.com, axes 2011-11-03</ref> A schrinjent rischrikshan de pah di yuus a di ieria faamali dimaakiet az di mask (we muotaim a onggl wah sumaal puoshan a di laaja komplex), ah, ina Izlamik [[Shariya|Shariya]] laa, afta wah ieria faamali dezigniet az mask, irimien so tel di [[Laas Jojment|Jojment Die]].<ref name="qaSunniPathFiqhMasjid"/>

Nof mask ab ilabaret [[Duom|duom]], [[Minaret|minaret]], ah praya aal, ina difrah-difrah stail a aachitecha. Mask arijiniet pah di [[Ariebian Peninsiula|Ariebian Peninsiula]], bot nou deh kiah fain ina aal inabit kantinent. Mask saab az plies we [[Muzlim|Muzlim]] kiah kom tugiada fi ''salat'' (big صلاة ''ṣalāt'', miinin "praya") azwel az senta fi infamieshan, edikieshan, ah dispyuut seklment. Di [[Imam|imam]] liid di kanggrigieshan ina praya.

